        </div>
        <br>
        <div class="nine centered text-center columns">
            
            <h4>The Shingo Alumni consists of individuals from a wide variety of organizations and industries around the world who have attended the Shingo workshop series.</h4>
        </div>
    </div>
    <br>
    <div class="row">
        <p>These individuals have distinguished themselves by applying what they learned in the workshops and implementing systems that help to drive their cultural transformation. A Shingo Alumâ€™s cultural transformation is highlighted by measured improvement in key performance indicators driven by the appropriate behaviors.</p>
