        <br>
        <p>If you are interested in joining this elite group, please click on the red button below to submit your application. Be prepared to share dates and locations of the required workshops, as well as information relating to any projects you have completed as a result of your workshop learnings.</p>
        <br>
        <div class="row text-center">
            <div class="large rounded btn" style="background: #2FA3F0"><a href="https://huntsmancrm.tfaforms.net/359029" target="_blank">Shingo Alumni Application</a></div>
        </div>
        <br>
        <br>
        <div class="row">               
                <table class="striped">
                    <div style="margin-bottom: 10px;">
                        <button class="med-btn-blue" onclick='changePage(`page1`)'>A - F</button>
                        <button class="med-btn-blue" onclick='changePage(`page2`)'>G - M</button>
                        <button class="med-btn-blue" onclick='changePage(`page3`)'>N - Z</button>
                        <p style="display: inline-block;">(Examiners filtered alphabetically by first name.)</p>
                    </div>
                    <thead>
                        <tr>
                            <th>Name</th>
                            <th>Title</th>
                            <th>Company</th>
                        </tr>
                    </thead>

                    <tbody id='page1' style='display: '>                
                                    {{#each recipients_A_to_F}}
                                        <tr>
                                            <td>{{name}}</td>
                                            <td>{{Title}}</td>
                                            <td>{{Account.Name}}</td>
                                        </tr> 
                                    {{/each}}                                       
                    </tbody>
                    <tbody id='page2' style='display:none'>                
                                    {{#each recipients_G_to_M}}
                                        <tr>
                                            <td>{{name}}</td>
                                            <td>{{Title}}</td>
                                            <td>{{Account.Name}}</td>
                                        </tr> 
                                    {{/each}}                                       
                    </tbody>
                    <tbody id='page3' style='display:none'>                
                                    {{#each recipients_N_to_Z}}
                                        <tr>
                                            <td>{{name}}</td>
                                            <td>{{Title}}</td>
                                            <td>{{Account.Name}}</td>
                                        </tr> 
                                    {{/each}}                                       
                    </tbody>
                </table>
            </div>
            <script>
                /* This function takes the id of a page as an input
                and changes that page's display to '', if the id does not
                match then the display is changed to none so that only the
                selected pages actually displays */

                function changePage(id) {
                   const pages = ['page1','page2','page3']
                   document.getElementById(id).style.display = ''
                   for(let i = 0; i < 4; i++) {
                       if(id != pages[i]) {
                           document.getElementById(pages[i]).style.display = 'none'
                       }
                   }
                }
            </script>
    </div>
  </article>
